  "description": "Bright neon candy theme for Pi.",
  "readme": "# @codella/pi-theme-candy\n\nBright neon candy theme for [Pi](https://pi.dev): hot bubblegum pink, electric cotton-candy blue, glowing mint, vivid lavender, strawberry, lemon, and cream on a deep licorice background.\n\n## Install\n\n```bash\npi install npm:@codella/pi-theme-candy\n```\n\n## Use\n\nSelect `candy` in `/settings`, or add it to your Pi settings:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"theme\": \"candy\"\n}\n```\n\n## Package contents\n\n```text\nthemes/candy.json\n```\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n",
